articles.title: About
articles.contents:
About the Project
Median Wages by Gender and Occupation was made through Kane’s Free High School Data
Science Bootcamp. This project visualizes how women are being paid
less than their male counterparts.
Goals
Illustrate the gap on wages by gender
Highlight inequality in the professional workforce
Git Hub Repository
Link: https://github.com/samnaik10/wages-by-gender
About Me
My name is Samruddhi Naik. I’m a rising freshman at
WPI in Massachusetts. I like sports, cooking, music, robotics and
computer science.
Contact Information
Git Hub: https://github.com/samnaik10
